</div>
```

**Scroll container structure:**
- Outer div: `"relative z-10 flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-4 pt-20"`
- Inner max-width container: `"relative mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl"`

**Width constraint:** `max-w-3xl` (768px) — **This is the bottleneck.**

