```

**This nested container has:**
- `"ml-10.75"` (left margin to align under the avatar)
- `"space-y-4"` (vertical spacing)
- **Inherits `max-w-3xl` from parent `OnboardingShell`**

#### **Chat.tsx** — `/Users/aryan/Projects/GAIA/gaia-onboarding-revamp/apps/web/src/features/onboarding/components/stages/Chat.tsx`

(Lines 126-136) — Final chat stage
