  style={{ contentVisibility: "auto", containIntrinsicSize: "0 120px" }}
>
  <div className="flex items-end gap-1">
    {!hideAvatar && (
      <div className="relative bottom-0 min-w-10 shrink-0">
        {showBubbleChrome && (
          <m.div className={...}>
            <Image alt="GAIA Logo" src={...} width={30} height={30} />
          </m.div>
        )}
      </div>
    )}

    <div className="chatbubblebot_parent flex-1">  // ← flex-1, grows to parent width
      <div className="flex w-full flex-col gap-2">
        <MemoryIndicator {...} />
        <div className="chat_bubble_container">{renderedComponent}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {showBubbleChrome && (
    <div className="ml-10.75 flex flex-col">
      {!!follow_up_actions && <FollowUpActions {...} />}
      {/* ... actions */}
    </div>
  )}

  {children}  // ← processingChecklist injected here
</div>
```

**Key classes:**
- Bubble wrapper: `"relative flex flex-col"` — no width constraint
- Avatar container: `"min-w-10 shrink-0"` — fixed 40px
- Parent container: `"chatbubblebot_parent flex-1"` — **grows to available width**
- Message container: `"chat_bubble_container"` — inherits full width

---

### 6. ONBOARDING CHAT STREAM (TOO DEMO)

#### **RevealTodos.tsx** — `/Users/aryan/Projects/GAIA/gaia-onboarding-revamp/apps/web/src/features/onboarding/components/stages/RevealTodos.tsx`

(Lines 128-142) — Run-now demo container
```tsx
if (state.todoExecutionStarted) {
  const selected = state.todoExecutionTodo;
  return (
    <m.div
      className="mt-10 ml-10.75 space-y-4 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-800/40 p-4 backdrop-blur-xl"  // ← Nested container
      initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
      animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
    >
      {selected && (
        <SelectedTodoIndicator
